Package: phylometacheck
Title: Check and Correct Sample Names between Phyloseq and Metadata
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Scott", "Handley", , "scott.handley@email.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools to identify and fix discrepancies between sample names in
    phyloseq objects and metadata files. Provides fuzzy matching algorithms
    to detect similar names and generates interactive reports with
    suggestions for standardization.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    stringdist,
    phyloseq,
    ggplot2,
    rmarkdown,
    DT,
    shiny,
    htmltools
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    patchwork
Config/testthat/edition: 3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/ScottHandley/phylometacheck
BugReports: https://github.com/ScottHandley/phylometacheck/issues
